721
00:57:30,208 --> 00:57:33,041
- [man 5] Guys, look there!
- [man 6] Hey, grandpa!

722
00:57:40,250 --> 00:57:41,250
[gunshot]

723
00:57:41,333 --> 00:57:42,333
[man 5] Go!

724
00:57:44,875 --> 00:57:45,875
What was it?

725
00:57:45,958 --> 00:57:47,041
[Declan] Carter!

726
00:57:51,083 --> 00:57:52,291
Carter!

727
00:57:54,375 --> 00:57:57,750
Listen to me.  I have to talk to you.

728
00:57:57,833 --> 00:57:58,833
Who is?

729
00:58:00,333 --> 00:58:02,250
[Declan] I want to help you, Carter.

730
00:58:02,833 --> 00:58:04,083
What happens?

731
00:58:13,458 --> 00:58:18,083
Okay, we have to leave.
Collect everything and follow me.

732
00:58:40,458 --> 00:58:43,208
- Follow me.  Are you ready?
- Yup.

733
00:58:43,291 --> 00:58:44,375
Here we go!

734
00:59:05,583 --> 00:59:06,583
Down, down!

735
00:59:26,416 --> 00:59:28,583
[coughing]

736
00:59:28,666 --> 00:59:30,916
Come on come on!
There is no more time, no oxygen.

737
00:59:30,958 --> 00:59:34,333
It's getting hot down here.
The fire is approaching.

738
00:59:34,416 --> 00:59:36,666
- We ended up in the pan.
- Yup.

739
00:59:37,375 --> 00:59:40,083
- Not in the pan, but on the stove.
- What are you talking about?

740
00:59:40,166 --> 00:59:43,500
- Relax, everything will be fine.
