763
01:02:43,375 --> 01:02:44,625
What you are doing?

764
01:02:46,541 --> 01:02:48,041
- Killian?
- Carter!

765
01:02:49,583 --> 01:02:51,791
- Do you receive me?
- Killian!

766
01:02:52,875 --> 01:02:56,291
- Thank God, you're alive!
- Yes, we're fine.

767
01:02:58,583 --> 01:03:02,041
We are at the old mine entrance.
