770
01:03:12,541 --> 01:03:14,833
- Fire?
- The seismic fire.

771
01:03:15,333 --> 01:03:18,583
- Is that what they call it?
- We use the dam.

772
01:03:18,666 --> 01:03:21,791
We can empty it all
and put out the fires.

773
01:03:21,875 --> 01:03:24,916
