involvement in the disaster.

826
01:06:36,708 --> 01:06:39,625
- Do not move!
- No, wait!  That's not how it went.

827
01:06:39,708 --> 01:06:43,208
- It was you!
- Look, don't do this.

828
01:06:43,291 --> 01:06:45,583
[TV] We will give five million
euros to anyone who finds it.

829
01:06:45,666 --> 01:06:48,750
I have five million
good reasons to do it.

830
01:06:48,833 --> 01:06:52,458
- Mom, we have to leave now.
- Don't go anywhere.

831
01:06:54,625 --> 01:06:58,250
[radio] To all units.
We're looking for Dr. Carter.  Caution.

832
01:06:58,333 --> 01:07:02,166
She could be armed.  She
was last seen driving a sidecar.

833
01:07:05,500 --> 01:07:07,083
- Throw it down!
- My God!

834
01:07:07,166 --> 01:07:10,875
- Mom, what do you want to do?  Come on let's go!
- Put it down!

835
01:07:10,958 --> 01:07:14,666
Come on, there's a five
million euro bounty on my head.

836
01:07:14,750 --> 01:07:17,666
I am dangerous!  Put it down!

837
01:07:26,000 --> 01:07:27,833
[shooting]

